org.msgpack.util
クラス TemplatePrecompiler

java.lang.Object
  org.msgpack.util.TemplatePrecompiler

public class TemplatePrecompiler
extends Object

This class is a template precompiler, which is used for saving templates that TemplateBuilder generated. It saves templates as .class files. Application enables to load the .class files and use templates.
